    <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
      <body> 
        <div rend="parallel">
            <p xml:id="Aink412-kilavi">ituvumatu.</p>
<p xml:lang="en">And this is that.</p>
</div>
        <div rend="parallel">
                <lg xml:id="Aink412">
<l>kāyā koṉṟai neytaṉ mullai</l>
<l>pōtaviḻ taḷavamoṭu piṭavalarntu kaviṉip</l>
<l>pūvaṇi koṇṭaṉṟāṟ puṟavē</l>
<l>pēramark kaṇṇi yāṭukam viraintē.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg xml:lang="en">
            <l>The ironwood, the laburnum, the water lily,the jasmine,</l>
            <l>along with the golden jasmine with opening buds and the <foreign xml:lang="ta-Latn">piṭavu</foreign></l> 
            <l>- the woodland blossoms, becoming beautiful, and takes the flowers as [its] ornaments.</l>
            <l>O you with large beuatiful eyes, let us hurry and bathe.</l>
                     
          </lg>
        </div>
      </body>
